data.description: Brick home with versatile floor plan. 3 bed 2 bath in main house and studio with full bath just across attached carport from main house. Large den/family room just off of the kitchen overlooking carport. Studio would be ideal for 4th bedroom, in law suite office etc. There is an attached carport between the main house and studio. Excellent location next door to Mobile Christian. Home needs a few updates and repairs but priced accordingly. Sold as is where is subject to court approval, title conveyed by statutory warranty deed. Allow 6 to 8 weeks for court approval and closing. Shown by appointment only. Home is occupied. Cash or conventional only. Home will not qualify for fha or va.
